document_data.mainbody: '''Stormwynd Dock''' was one of the wharves located in the [[Baldur's Gate/Lower City|Lower City]] of [[Baldur's Gate]].
document_data.Location: Stormwynd Dock and its four legs could be found just south from the [[Stormshore Street Dock]] in the [[Baldur's Gate/Brampton|Brampton]] district. It was the closest major dock to the [[Cliffgate]].
